    "user_script": "// Steel blue (low) to cool grey-white (high).\n// MIDI note 68 (A♭4) is the repeating raindrop — highlighted icy blue.\nfor(let n=0;n<128;n++){\n  if(n===68){\n    api.setNote(n,80,200,255);\n  } else {\n    const t=Math.max(0,Math.min(1,(n-21)/87));\n    api.setNote(n,\n      Math.round(30+t*120),\n      Math.round(50+t*140),\n      Math.round(160+t*80)\n    );\n  }\n}",
